{
  "stem": "12053.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we feel-- all of us feel-- a guilt complex, as opposed to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have their meetings in the Holocaust Survivors Center.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I wonder if they call us Holocaust survivors?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are survivors, of course, but we haven't gone through the holocaust.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- [INAUDIBLE] we're quite friendly together but we do not mix.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nor with the hidden children, because it would be too big.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cannot encompass every-- anything so vast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there are-- there were 10,000-- nearly 10,000 of us, I have found worldwide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would think we have found-- and a lot of us have died in the last few years-- we have found about three and a half thousand, which is a lot after 50 years.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they are worldwide.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we are too big to amalgamate with the hidden children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I put the idea into their heads that they should also write a book of reminiscences because it's very, very important.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and the survivors, the Holocaust survivors, are a group on their own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We are the Kindertransportees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we, although we're very friendly and we-- we talk-- I recommend them as speakers, and they recommend me as speakers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I spend my life now speaking to a lot-- last year I was in-- in South Africa sponsored by the-- the equivalent of the JIA in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I go a lot to Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At first it was very painful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I've been now four times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they receive me with open arms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the new Germans, I must say-- the ones who want to know, the schools I've spoken to-- They are more interested than the schools in England.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't get enough invitations from schools in England.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, I've never had an invitation from an English school.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
